Like it or not AJ is better as a face not a heel.
Becky is probably the best women’s wrestler ever, for a start how many others in the women’s division would shake off a bleeding nose and bruised eye socket and still stay standing in the crowd and not go to the medics (breaking WWE rules)
AJ is the best guy they have.
They never had the “landed on his feet, roll through” until he came along. Only a few wrestlers are good enough to remember how to take the Styles clash - so they made him go with the elbow. They’ve made him cut about 1/3 of his offensive moves because other wrestlers can’t keep up. When he comes out for a singles match he gets a crowd pop.
TNA fell apart when he left. ROH struggled when he left, even NJW would like him back.
WWE need to make more of having him, they don’t want AEW getting him or they’ll just be boosting their competitions ratings.
